==English==

===Etymology===
Possibly a shortening of {{m|en|[[attractor]] [[beam]]}}; note however the broader meaning of {{m|en|tractor|gloss=machinery that pulls something}}. {{coin|en|w=E. E. Smith|E. E. "Doc" Smith|nobycat=1|nat=American|occ=writer}} in his 1931 novel ''[[wikipedia:Spacehounds of IPC|Spacehounds of IPC]]'', first serialised in ''Amazing Stories''.

